      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
