    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of showroom quality. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in factory condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and that signature 'new car' scent persists. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a fully documented service history from authorized dealerships and exceptionally low mileage. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been pampered since day one. No accidents, no smoking, and absolutely no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, currently maintained in pristine showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning clientele, featuring an unblemished exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Rigorously inspected to ensure peak mechanical performance, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality and distinction. Experience the standard of luxury and reliability that only a vehicle of this caliber can provide.",
      "price": 48500.0,
