    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It has been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously maintained, and not a single scratch to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for the road, this is the one for you. Come by and take a look, I promise you're going to love it!",
