    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical state is impeccable: the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been structurally reinforced for long-term track or street durability. Power is sent through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and linear power delivery. The chassis remains stiff and responsive, supported by a pristine suspension assembly with no bushing deflection. Finished with concours-level paint depth and an interior free of typical bolster wear, this specimen is a turnkey investment for the serious collector.",
